org.ggp.base.util.logging

Class GamerLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ggp.base.util.logging.GamerLogger

  • public class GamerLogger
extends java.lang.Object
    GamerLogger is a customized logger designed for long-running game players. Logs are written to directories on a per-game basis. Each logfile represents a single logical component of the game playing program, identified whenever the logger is called. TODO: More details about specific use examples.
